YAOUNDE, Cameroon, April 13, 2018/APO Group/ -- 
                                                
                        Global Affairs Canada today issued the following statement:





“Canada is saddened by the tragic military plane crash that occurred in Algeria yesterday, which has claimed the lives of 257 people.

 “As an international partner and a friend, Canada stands with the people of Algeria as they grieve and offers its deepest sympathies to all those affected by this tragedy.”